Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.60,0:01:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是只屬於我的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.04,0:01:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ喜歡秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹喜歡ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.31,0:01:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.76,0:02:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#24         只屬於ちぃ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.87,0:02:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.77,0:02:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.01,0:02:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又聽到聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.68,0:02:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…聲音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.08,0:02:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳們兩個怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.02,0:02:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.06,0:02:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.60,0:02:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.70,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.75,0:02:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.85,0:02:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於ちぃ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.54,0:03:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非做不可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.07,0:03:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與另一個我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.61,0:03:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.92,0:03:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬！柚姬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們醒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.44,0:03:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.75,0:04:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.42,0:04:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ最重要的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.79,0:04:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ心 中最特別的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.26,0:04:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於ちぃ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟能直接傳入CPU中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.06,0:04:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位小姐與所有的電腦連線了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們雖然被設計成\N不受那股力量影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其實我們還是架構在\N同一系統下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管對手是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.94,0:04:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在事態變得無法收拾之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟能將戴特的攻擊程式\N反彈回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能駭進的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就直接連線吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我要阻止妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.71,0:05:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快放開ちぃ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.12,0:05:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在對ちぃ做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.96,0:05:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了阻止這位小姐\N而被製造出來的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.63,0:05:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這台危險的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.73,0:05:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉瑪，你不需要對\N不相干的人解釋這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是不相干的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是“只屬於我的人”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.14,0:05:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當她決定“只屬於我的人”時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.58,0:05:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會與全世界的電腦連線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.38,0:05:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並啟動某個程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ做了什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.56,0:05:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會做什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這連我資料庫裡也沒有記載
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.29,0:06:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是\N為了停止她而被製造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.00,0:06:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得將程式停止\N並讓她永不能再度執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.40,0:06:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將OS破壞，並停止一切機能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.41,0:06:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要將她消滅掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.17,0:06:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！快住手啊！\Nちぃ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛為一台電腦這麼認真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的人就將在眼前被摧毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也會這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.12,0:06:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦是不會有那種情感的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.03,0:06:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與電腦戀愛\N是不會有結果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.76,0:06:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦與人類是不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.14,0:06:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是人類還是電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都不重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.31,0:06:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我其他的誰都不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡上ちぃ了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.02,0:06:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.43,0:07:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.43,0:07:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉瑪，你在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.13,0:07:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.74,0:07:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，他們兩人的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.11,0:07:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及，電腦的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非做不可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.05,0:07:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與另一個我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.82,0:07:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ最重要的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ心 中最特別的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.26,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於ちぃ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.58,0:07:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ！ちぃ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.53,0:08:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.56,0:09:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.69,0:09:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是芙蕾雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.25,0:09:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CPU、硬碟、系統一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉瑪你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.83,0:09:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬，妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.47,0:09:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有 發生異常嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個聲音嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.94,0:10:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.74,0:10:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很悲哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.55,0:10:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.89,0:10:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們都醒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.59,0:10:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是…那個聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾雅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.41,0:10:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳會在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.75,0:10:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾雅…那ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.15,0:10:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.75,0:10:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且ちぃ她之前\N不是叫“愛爾塔”嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾雅不是因為愛上妳丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而消失了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.60,0:11:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我因為心 痛而動彈不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.64,0:11:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我覺得已經撐不下去時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.41,0:11:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到我這裡來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在芙蕾雅消失前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將芙蕾雅的心 放到我裡面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.92,0:11:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我幫妳守護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我幫妳守護妳的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到我裡面來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳在那裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.24,0:11:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷，ちぃ她怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對電腦不太了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.12,0:11:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.09,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ找到了“只屬於我的人”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.36,0:12:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到後\N明明還有事情得去完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.13,0:12:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她卻半途而癈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.84,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放棄了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.87,0:12:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白就算電腦喜歡上人\N卻仍有辦不到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.25,0:12:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算“只屬於我的人”喜歡上我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.49,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是無法幫他任何忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些都沒關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.29,0:12:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是人類還是電腦\N那種事一點都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.89,0:12:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡上ちぃ了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，ちぃ卻不這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.50,0:12:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳聽得見嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在那裡面對吧，快出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.21,0:12:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾雅，ちぃ她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.41,0:12:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也無法讀取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.12,0:13:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽，拜託妳\N將我們處分掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說些什麼啊，芙蕾雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.96,0:13:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前很喜歡爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心 痛到動彈不得時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.50,0:13:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾想瞞著媽媽向他表白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我卻說不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.54,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們真是失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.86,0:13:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？Chobits？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.23,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密碼聲紋比對完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳打算做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.31,0:14:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來那程式可以不用啟動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.51,0:14:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，您有什麼命令？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.29,0:14:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刪除資料，及停止系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.32,0:14:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ別做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.79,0:14:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確定要刪除資料\N及停止系統嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.33,0:14:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.07,0:14:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啊，ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.14,0:14:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.15,0:14:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作業結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.13,0:14:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.97,0:14:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.47,0:15:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.94,0:15:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那組密碼只會對\N我與我丈夫的聲紋產生反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.64,0:15:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來ちぃ真的很愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.52,0:15:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才自己離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.95,0:15:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.69,0:15:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後還是讓你留下痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.66,0:15:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.30,0:15:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原以為如果是他\N或許有辦法改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.28,0:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.72,0:15:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.29,0:15:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不了解ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.06,0:15:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此讓ちぃ感到痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.43,0:16:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有好好的教導ちぃ\N什麼才是“幸福”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.63,0:16:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果ちぃ還在某處的話\N能幫我轉告她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.77,0:16:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的“幸福”就是\N能與喜歡的人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.04,0:16:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起\N雖然會有許多痛苦與悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.85,0:16:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過若無法在一起\N將會是更痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.39,0:16:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓ちぃ得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.94,0:16:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾有過一段悲傷的往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今胸口仍會感到悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.22,0:16:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常非常悲傷的往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明失去了重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.32,0:17:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的痛苦卻仍殘留著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是繼續的尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.93,0:17:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是我，所以他喜歡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.01,0:17:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後，我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.91,0:17:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是更加痛苦的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都幫不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.75,0:17:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在他身旁只會感到痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.46,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到痛苦的他\N自己也會感到痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.46,0:17:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定從他面前消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為喜歡他所以我消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.74,0:17:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但看不到他反而更加痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.08,0:17:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見不到他將會更加更加痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.52,0:18:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是因為喜歡他而分開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.02,0:18:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳明明喜歡他\N卻要跟他分開嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.46,0:18:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那會讓他得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是幸福？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.60,0:18:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸福…那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.49,0:18:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是妳所謂的幸福嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.49,0:18:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的幸福就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.60,0:18:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的幸福只能從他身上找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.73,0:18:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算感到痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.70,0:18:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算感到心 痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.74,0:18:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此，我還是只要他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.15,0:19:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.77,0:19:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又聽到那聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.67,0:19:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過與剛剛的不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.21,0:19:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘴溫暖又溫柔的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳們兩個！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉瑪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道那女孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.93,0:19:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了，我馬上幫你檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在臉紅什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.46,0:20:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ是電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ不是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有辦不到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.20,0:20:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.63,0:20:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是ちぃ想跟秀樹在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.10,0:20:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.01,0:20:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想跟ちぃ在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.72,0:20:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.09,0:20:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮有許多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.09,0:20:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮有許多那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.26,0:21:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都喜歡上他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也都被他人所愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.57,0:21:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,許多人\N以及許多的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，你還想再落榜嗎？\N居住在許多地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.01,0:21:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.68,0:21:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人從許多的人\N與許多的那個之中找到了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.92,0:21:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並喜歡上我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.76,0:21:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺，茶幫您泡好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.12,0:21:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在在這裡\N謝謝妳，柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.33,0:21:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與他一起在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.97,0:21:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2，3，4\N我們很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.98,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.31,0:21:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.08,0:21:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.00,0:22:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也有人墜入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.58,0:22:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在世界的某個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.98,0:22:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩條線就算糾纏在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.65,0:22:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仍然被解開         永遠不會結合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.53,0:22:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是遲鈍的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.90,0:22:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法以言語完全表達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.54,0:22:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看         微風輕撫         長髮飛舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.91,0:22:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間顫抖         兩人搖晃著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.09,0:23:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後         又有人墜入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.49,0:23:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信著永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.79,0:23:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉，本須和是怎麼樣的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.79,0:23:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.53,0:23:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會突然大聲叫喊的可怕的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.36,0:23:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他總是很亢奮嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.93,0:23:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.87,0:23:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人喃喃自語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.84,0:23:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或突然在房間滾來滾去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.94,0:23:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個行為詭異的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.71,0:23:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.81,0:23:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼結論是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.04,0:24:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.04,0:24:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我笑不出來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.38,0:24:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits         下一回\N「新保、絲茉茉         談論」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，我跟那傢伙是朋友嗎？
